Set Height 750
Source "recordings/tapes/shared-config.tape"
Output "recordings/svgs/toolkits/list-query-gmail-limit-1.svg"
Output "recordings/ascii/toolkits/list-query-gmail-limit-1.ascii"

Hide
Type "# Combine --query and --limit"
Enter
Show
Type "composio toolkits list --query 'gmail' --limit 1"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 6s
